{
  "stem": "7093.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I checked up, and she confirmed it that this woman was absolutely, viciously anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Then our head teacher, our class head teacher, was anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And the funny thing was that it turned out the she was actually a baptized Jewess.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And she was deported just the same.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But she was pretty anti-Semitic and pretty nasty as well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And especially with me, because the other girls, they were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I was-- I was an outsider.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "My whole life, I was somehow an outsider.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I'm still an outsider in a way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I, I was-- because I was always extremely outspoken.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I always believed in the truth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And you always say the truth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And you shout it, not only say it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And people didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And you also shouted you are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And in Hungary, you didn't talk about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I mean, if you were Jewish, you keep quiet about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "It's not very nice to be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "I mean, one is Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And one keeps the festivals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And one goes to synagogue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "But one doesn't speak about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "But I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "I didn't go to synagogue, but I did-- unless I had to-- but I did speak about my being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And I stood up for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And anybody who attacked me, I, I really viciously attacked back because of that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "But and, and therefore, this teacher, of course, hated me because she hated my, my outspoken Jewishness.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "I became, as I said, I was a Zionist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "At the age of 16, I was a Zionist leader.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And I was even sent to another town, which was called Sopron, which is also on the border of, of Hu-- of Austria, to open a new hall for the Zionists there, for the Zionist youth there.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
